title: TutsPlus - Advanced Photoshop Techniques
description: So you have mastered the basics of Photoshop, are you ready for the next step? Join in as Howard Pinsky of IceFlowStudios teaches us how to master the more advanced topics in Photoshop. In this course, Howard will walk you through many of the advanced tools and techniques of Photoshop professionals, creating your own actions and shortcuts, and look at using Photoshop in specific contexts and projects.
